#

Mediterranean Chicken Grain Bowl

30 min
$10
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinMediterraneanGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Main CourseLunchDinner

Tags:

HealthyQuick MealEasy

Description

A vibrant and nutritious bowl filled with tender chicken, fluffy grains, and fresh Mediterranean flavors.

Ingredients

  • cooked quinoa or brown rice: 1 cup
  • grilled chicken breast, sliced: 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes, halved: 1/2 cup
  • cucumber, diced: 1/2 cup
  • kalamata olives, pitted and halved: 1/4 cup
  • feta cheese, crumbled: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • salt and pepper: to taste
